      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F0B42410-22F5-0135-133D-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Compose</strong> icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select-course" data-step-uuid="e9a96fb0-3543-4abe-8ab1-3673b69406b6">
    <h2 id="select-course" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Course</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/281/original/9730fd09-2d59-4cad-896a-9d014cd1b68d.png" srcset="" alt="Select Course" height="459" width="755">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_ea9b35d8-fb36-4253-a5f6-c2ad30c1286e" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Course</strong> drop-down menu [1], then select the course name [2]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_users" data-step-uuid="940e9e5a-4b62-45ef-a7f0-583d19fa827a">
    <h2 id="add_users" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Users</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/308/original/3ebe4942-1fca-4040-ac4f-4db321153354.png" srcset="" alt="Add Users" height="94" width="755">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F0B47E90-22F5-0135-1341-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To add a user, you can search for the user in the <strong>To</strong> field [1] or use the <strong>Address Book</strong> [2]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="search-for-users" data-step-uuid="1bc528ed-5ad0-4f68-bae0-5461352449f8">
    <h3 id="search-for-users" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Search for Users</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/285/original/2cca2812-43e2-41a1-8ae7-c2110a93c47c.png" srcset="" alt="Search for Users" height="138" width="755">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_56f1a55f-33e2-42a1-87cf-a3ec6ccf2cb9" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To search for a user, type the user's name in the <strong>To</strong> field [1]. Canvas automatically populates matching names. Select the user's name [2]. </p>
<p>To send a message to multiple users, type the names of additional users in the To field.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="filter_group" data-step-uuid="7082daab-c2d1-4a3b-a4bc-46e9c543432c">
    <h2 id="filter_group" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Student Groups</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/287/original/7af78f02-e5f6-4cfb-ac28-de3071e1e50a.png" srcset="" alt="View Student Groups" height="725" width="755">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F0B450E0-22F5-0135-133F-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view and add a user in a student group, click the <strong>Address Book</strong> button [1], then the <strong>Student Groups </strong>option [2]. Select the group name [3]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="use_group_roster" data-step-uuid="43905751-b83d-48af-af68-32840f88e3ed">
    <h2 id="use_group_roster" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Group Member</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/290/original/15612781-2a93-431c-b4d8-6094405358b4.png" srcset="" alt="Add Group Member" height="301" width="779">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F0B506C0-22F5-0135-1345-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Group members' names display in alphabetical order by last name. Select the user's name which you would like to add to the message [1]. </p>
<p>To send a message to multiple users, navigate back to the group member list by clicking the <strong>Address Book</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="send_message" data-step-uuid="ab550132-c89a-40f2-aec9-32132373d65a">
    <h2 id="send_message" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Send Message</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/643/292/original/270c89fa-62c2-4b4f-815a-9af021aff49b.png" srcset="" alt="Send Message" height="670" width="796">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F0B53570-22F5-0135-1347-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the <strong>Subject</strong> field [1], enter a subject line for your message.</p>
<p>If you are sending your message to multiple users, but you do not want each user to see who else was included in the message, click the <strong>Send an individual message to each recipient</strong> checkbox [2]. Â If your message includes over 100 recipients (including you as the sender), this checkbox is selected by default.</p>
<p>In the message field [3], type your message. All content is sent in plain text. URLs included in a message automatically become clickable links after the message is sent.</p>
<p>If you want to include an attachment or media file, click the <strong>Attachment</strong> or <strong>Media File</strong> buttons [4].</p>
<p>When you are finished, click the <strong>Send </strong>button [5].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
